<br />\n<br />\n港股重上三萬點絕非天荒夜談，因「美中經濟與安全審查委員報告」被港股市場認為是個正面事件，對今天及將來的營商環境都有利。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一旦取消與美國的關係，不排除發展至令到我國更加信任或扶持香港，在取消香港關係法後，我國只需派遣北水3萬億元來港買股票，便足以掃起港股三千點，以我國13億人口計算，救港北水資金每名中國人僅付出2044元人民幣，對我的國而言實在太小數目。</span></span>事實上，近期港股觸底後有強力支持，加上騰訊（700）業績被市場認為是好，本身已有反彈條件。<br />\n<br />\n至於標普點解要見個位數？因為近期股評界潮流興閒閒地都跌八成，雖然一般內文冇交代原因，但標題唔寫見個位數，呢篇文恐怕冇人見到，所以惟有將標普500指數首站目標價定喺9點，現價計跌99.67%，順應潮流，冇乜特別原因。<br />\n<br />\n高明<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bigricetea/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbigricetea%2F&d=6tuXhv1Op5ZcMF%2FNsQcJwLDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=2d84471c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bigricetea/</a><br />\n<br />\n全球樓行 Dream House零距離<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/overseasproperty\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Foverseasproperty&d=6tuXhv1Op5ZcMF%2FNsQcJwLDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=606bcd46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Foverseasproperty&h=9bc132df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/overseasproperty</a><br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181118/58927809\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181118%2F58927809&d=6tuXhv1Op5ZcMF%2FNsQcJwLDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=5c68c46f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181118%2F58927809&h=725d8aa5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181118/58927809</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img